WEBVTT

00:00:28.394 --> 00:00:31.108
da se mase ne da ustvariti

00:00:31.108 --> 00:00:32.272
niti uničiti,

00:00:32.272 --> 00:00:33.942
kar pomeni, da se junakova masa

00:00:33.942 --> 00:00:37.882
ne bo spremenila, tudi če se on poveča.

00:00:37.882 --> 00:00:42.236
Recimo, ko spečemo rahel biskvit,

00:00:42.236 --> 00:00:44.064
je okusen pečeni posladek

00:00:44.064 --> 00:00:46.691
veliko večji od testa,

00:00:46.691 --> 00:00:48.206
ki smo ga dali v pečico,

00:00:48.206 --> 00:00:50.826
a teža testa bi morala ostati enaka

00:00:50.826 --> 00:00:52.001
teži peciva,

00:00:52.001 --> 00:00:55.695
če dodamo izparelo vlago.

00:00:55.695 --> 00:00:56.978
V kemijskih enačbah

00:00:56.978 --> 00:00:59.589
se molekule razporedijo v nove spojine,

00:00:59.589 --> 00:01:03.282
a izgubiti se ne sme nobena.